          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Social Security Integrity Act of 2015</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Commissioner of Social Security to implement all of the recommendations described in the memorandum from the Office of the Inspector General of the Social Security Administration entitled &quot;Numberholders Age 112 or Older Who Did Not Have a Death Entry on the Numident (A-06-14-34030)&quot; and dated March 4, 2015.</p>]]></text>
